# NOTE: crates/core/models/{model.onnx,tokenizer.json} are committed as EMPTY
# placeholders so the `onnx` feature compiles. When you drop in the real
# multi-megabyte weights locally, do NOT commit them — e.g.
#   git update-index --skip-worktree crates/core/models/model.onnx
# to keep the large file out of git.
